data.name: Commands.NewDir.Description
data.value: Creates a new specified directory with specified parameters.

data.name: Exceptions.DirectoryNotSpecified
data.value: The directory to be created was not specified. If this was not intentional, ensure that you are passing a valid directory as an argument.

data.name: Exceptions.InvalidArgument
data.value: An invalid argument value was passed to the application. The invalid argument value was {x}.

data.name: Exceptions.DirectoryNotSpecified.Plural
data.value: One of the directories to be created was not specified. If this was not intentional, ensure that you are passing valid directories as an argument.

data.name: Commands.ManyNewDir.Description
data.value: Creates new specified directories with specified parameters.
